I am SHERLOCKED!!This is what brilliance on TV is all about! This series is brilliant in all terms: acting, casting, plot,writing, cinematography, direction, production, editing, score, location! It is so attentively executed that is nothing less than perfection. Intelligent, genius, sophisticated, mind-blowing, thought-provoking is just a few words among many others that I would use to describe it. It is so well written and so well acted that is amazing!Congratulations to all for making 'Sherlock', cast and crew! And I must say that Benedict Cumberbatch is truly an amazing actor!Impeccable acting as Sherlock! I would recommend 'Sherlock' to everyone!It is a MUST-see!You won't be disappointed!You will be amazed by the series!Definitely one of the greatest series!